# ─── SECURITY: credential exposure prevention ─────────────────────────────
# This repo is PUBLIC on GitHub. Anything matching the patterns below must
# never be committed. If you add a new credential file, add a pattern here
# (and the pre-commit hook in .husky/pre-commit blocks credential-shaped
# strings even when files aren't ignored).

# Environment files (all variants)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.env
.env.local
.env.development.local
.env.test.local
.env.production.local

# Service account / admin SDK keys
serviceAccountKey.json
*-serviceAccountKey.json
firebase-adminsdk-*.json
scripts/.service-account.json
scripts/.secrets/

# Private keys + certificates
*.pem
*.key

# Browser profile dirs (may persist auth cookies/tokens)
/tests/smoke/.profiles/

# ─── Build + tooling ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
logs/
/emulator-data/
/test-results/
/playwright-report/
/.firebase/
/.claude/settings.local.json
/.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
/firebase-debug.log
/firestore-debug.log
/pubsub-debug.log
/.claude/state/dev-server.log
/.claude/state/dev-server.err.log
/.claude/state/preview-server.log
/.claude/state/preview-server.err.log
# Transient E2E/emulator gate-run diagnostic logs (scratch output, regenerated each sweep)
/.claude/state/e2e-*.log
/.claude/state/emu-*.log
/tests/smoke/output/

# Pre-watcher-test artifacts (remove after test rollback)
/.claude/state/cron-paused.json.bak-test
/.test-rollback-target

# ─── Cron / watcher routine state (must not dirty working tree) ───────────
# Per AUTONOMOUS_FAILURE_RECOVERY v8.3: routine cron output must NEVER dirty
# the tree, or the downloads-watcher preflight refuses to apply Founder
# decisions. The watcher cursor + tests/round-trip-workspace/ are scratch
# artifacts that re-create themselves on every run; they must never block
# the apply path.
/.claude/state/proposals/.last-processed-decisions.json
/.claude/state/proposals/inbox/
/.claude/state/amendments/inbox/
/.claude/state/amendments/inbox-archive/
/.claude/state/founder/inbox/
/.claude/state/escalations/inbox/
/.claude/state/quota-status.json
/tests/round-trip-workspace/

# DASH video segments + harness from main-flows-v2 x-probe (scratch source
# material; the static PNG frames in the same directory are the tracked
# reference deliverables).
/.claude/state/main-flows-v2/reference-frames/_harness.html
/.claude/state/main-flows-v2/reference-frames/*.mp4
/.claude/state/main-flows-v2/reference-frames/*.m4s
scripts/__pycache__/
tests/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc

# 2026-05-21 repo cleanup: visual-audit output PNGs are regenerable artifacts,
# not source. Keep .mjs sources, gitignore the PNGs + JSON outputs.
scripts/visual-audit/2026-*/
scripts/visual-audit/*.png
.claude/state/visual-audit-*/
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/reference-frames/*.png
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/reference-frames/*.jpg
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/iter*/
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/*.png
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/*.jpg
# design-iteration capture PNGs are regenerable via scripts/visual-audit/*.mjs;
# keep the .mjs sources tracked, gitignore the binary output (pre-2026-06 dirs
# stay grandfathered-tracked — gitignore never untracks).
.claude/state/design-iteration/2026-06-*/**/*.png
.claude/state/user-journey-audits/
.claude/state/dashboard-audit-*/**/*.png
.claude/state/dashboard-audit-*/screenshots/
.claude/state/app-audit-*/**/*.png
.claude/state/bug-investigation-*/**/*.png
.claude/state/audit-2026-*/**/*.png
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/iter-*-side-by-side.html
.claude/state/main-flows-v2/*-visual-review.md
# Bug triage cron output (regenerable)
.claude/state/aggregates/bug-triage-latest.json

# Repo secret scan output — regenerable; pre-commit hook flags excerpts
.claude/state/security/repo-secret-scan-latest.json
.claude/state/security/bundle-scan-latest.json

# Per AMD-020 auto-clean — exclude Python bytecode caches from tree
.playwright-mcp/

# Git worktrees — sibling-agent EnterWorktree adds these as linked working
# trees. They appear as gitlinks (mode 160000) in the parent index, which
# causes the parent's "git diff HEAD" to flag them as modified whenever the
# linked worktree's own checkout is dirty (-dirty suffix). The downloads-
# watcher's auto-commit gate cannot resolve that — committing the gitlink
# updates the ref but the linked tree's internal dirt persists. Ignore the
# directory entirely; worktrees remain functional via .git/worktrees/.
.claude/worktrees/

# ─── Dashboard reports: local-only per Founder directive 2026-05-14 ─────
# Dashboards in docs/reports/ are operational tooling for Founder's local
# view only. Repo is PUBLIC on GitHub; committing dashboards exposes
# proposal text, telemetry, agent activity to anyone with the repo URL.
# Founder directive: "only I should have access to dashboard and it
# should all be local not shared for anyone else to see".
#
# Regen pipeline (post-commit hook + cron) still writes these files; they
# just stay local. Existing dashboards in git history are NOT removed by
# this — that's a separate decision (filter-branch / BFG).
/docs/reports/dashboard.html
/docs/reports/amendments.html
/docs/reports/proposals.html
/docs/reports/escalations.html
/docs/reports/activity.html
/docs/reports/token-usage.html
/docs/reports/discussion-bubbles.html
/docs/reports/design-system.html
/docs/reports/main-flows.html
/docs/reports/index.html
/docs/reports/_assets/
/docs/reports/daily/
/docs/reports/ships/
/docs/reports/waves/
/docs/reports/weekly/
dist/
.lighthouseci/
.claude/state/aggregates/lighthouse/*.json
!.claude/state/aggregates/lighthouse-scores.json

# Visual-gate screenshots (per-run output, not source)
.claude/state/visual-gate/

# Critique probe artifacts (debugging tools)
.claude/state/critique/probe-*.mjs
.claude/state/critique/founder-checklist-expanded.png
.claude/state/critique/founder-checklist-real.png
.claude/state/critique/founder-checklist-screenshot.png
.claude/state/critique/sessions-real.png
.claude/state/sessions-watch.log

# Stop hook logs (session-end markers, not source)
.claude/state/stop-verification/

# 2026-05-21 (post-INC-002): files regenerated EVERY post-commit by the regen
# pipeline itself, causing infinite dirty-tree pulse. They're computed on-demand
# by the dashboard at file:// from source-of-truth state, so untracking them is
# safe — the dashboard regenerates them as needed.
.claude/state/aggregates/dashboard-freshness.json
.claude/state/aggregates/dashboard-smoke-latest.json
.claude/state/heartbeats/regen-all-last-pass.json
.claude/state/heartbeats/watcher-last-run.json

# 2026-05-22 (post-INC-002 chronic-pulse fix): files re-written by every cron
# cycle / regen / post-commit. They are LOCAL caches the aggregators recompute
# from source data. Tracking them caused 800+ commits per file of pure pulse
# noise + "still dirty" cycles. Untracked here so the tree converges to clean.
docs/reports/founder-checklist.html
docs/reports/sessions.html
.claude/state/telemetry/aggregates/current-snapshot.json
.claude/state/telemetry/aggregates/token-usage-snapshot.json
.claude/state/telemetry/aggregates/.token-usage-cursor.json
.claude/state/telemetry/events/*.ndjson
# 2026-05-22 chronic-pulse-fix: locally-computed aggregator caches. Each regen
# cycle rewrites these; tracking them caused 500-900 commits per file of pure
# pulse noise. They are recomputed from source files (proposals/, amendments/,
# escalations/, ship-progress/, telemetry/manual-quota-log.ndjson, etc.) so
# fresh checkouts regenerate them via the cron pipeline.
.claude/state/aggregates/*.json
.claude/state/heartbeats/*.json
.claude/state/heartbeat/*.log

# Lighthouse audit output (regen-able)
.lighthouseci-live/
.lighthouseci/

# 2026-05-29: transient/local evidence artifacts (not deliverables). Root-level
# E2E sweep log is regenerated each run; boot-smoke + critique-resume PNGs are
# local V1 evidence that stays out of the PUBLIC repo (matches visual-gate +
# critique-probe ignore policy above).
/.pw-*.log
/.agentshield-*.log
/staging-boot-smoke-*.png
/critique-*.png
.claude/state/critique-resume-*/

# Transient design-verification scratch dir + loose root capture PNGs
# (regenerable via scripts/visual-audit/*.mjs; stay out of the PUBLIC repo).
/scratch/
/depth-swatch*.png
/staging-*.png
/.claude/state/research/intro-iterations/
